11. Compression Layer

Compression is where intelligence happens.

11.1 Compression Goals
	•	reduce redundancy
	•	preserve anomalies
	•	expose invariants
	•	separate pattern from ornament
	•	produce actionable summaries

11.2 Compression Outputs

Every Raven cycle should attempt to return:
	•	raw observations
	•	clusters
	•	candidate invariants
	•	deltas
	•	counterexamples
	•	confidence estimate
	•	recommended state action

11.3 Compression Failure Modes
