	•	privileging elegance over accuracy

⸻

12. Pantheon Gating Layer

The gate prevents epistemic corruption.

12.1 Gate Questions

Before a state update:
	1.	Is the signal independent or recursive?
	2.	Does it improve prediction?
	3.	Does it survive contradiction?
	4.	Does it generalize beyond one domain?
	5.	Is this a genuine delta or noise?
	6.	Does it violate ethical constraints?
	7.	What would falsify this update?

12.2 Gate Outcomes
	•	promote — update StateVector
	•	quarantine — store as tentative
	•	reject — discard
	•	probe further — deploy more Ravens

