13. StateVector

The Raven Network should update a tracked epistemic state, not just output text.

13.1 Minimal StateVector Fields
	•	active hypotheses
	•	confidence weights
	•	open anomalies
	•	confirmed invariants
	•	known blind spots
	•	recent deltas
	•	update history
	•	unresolved tensions

13.2 State Update Rule

Do not update from:
	•	one source
	•	one vibe
	•	one dramatic anomaly

Prefer updates when:
	•	multiple independent Ravens agree
	•	signal improves future prediction
	•	contradiction pressure has been applied

