18. Failure Modes

18.1 Echo Loop

Ravens only return what the operator already believes.

18.2 Narrative Capture

Compression forces a story before evidence warrants it.

18.3 Over-Compression

Important anomalies are lost.

18.4 Signal Flood

Too much retrieval, not enough discrimination.

18.5 False Phase Transition

Random clustering mistaken for deep structural change.

18.6 Update Thrashing

StateVector changes too often and loses stability.

18.7 Shadow Blindness

Only visible content is tracked; absences are ignored.

