20. Minimal Operational Protocol

Step 1: Define query

What are you actually trying to learn?

Step 2: Define signal classes

What counts as relevant signal?

Step 3: Deploy multiple Raven types

At minimum:
	•	one direct
	•	one contrast
	•	one shadow
	•	one drift

Step 4: Aggregate

Cluster, deduplicate, score.

Step 5: Compress

Extract:
	•	invariants
	•	deltas
	•	anomalies
	•	candidate updates

Step 6: Gate

Apply falsification, ethics, and prediction checks.

Step 7: Update StateVector

Only if signal survives pressure.

Step 8: Log and version

Preserve history.

